        "end": null,
        "text": "通过量化对比，一目了然。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 103
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "数据这块，也是极度量化。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 104
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "有skill的通过率100%，无skill基线9%，差值91.5%。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 105
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "费用上，有skill每次大约4000token，无skill1750token，差了2250。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 106
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "但这是skill带来的额外消耗，对比产出的结果，值得。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 107
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "但评估的价值远不止于此。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 108
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "Anthropic官方也举了个例子。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 109
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "他们有个PDF skill，之前在处理表格时会出错。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 110
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "Claude需要把文字精确的放在特定坐标上，但因为没有明确的字段做引导，经常放歪。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 111
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "这个问题在评估过程中被发现，再进行修复改进定位逻辑后，问题就解决了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 112
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "也就是说，找到问题之后不用从头来过。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 113
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "评估结果会存在本地，下次你用skill-creator改进这个skill的时候，它会把上次标注的问题直接带进去，针对那里改。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 114
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "改完再跑一遍评估，看有没有提升。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 115
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "测试、发现、修、再测，这个循环是完整的。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 116
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "Anthropic把软件开发的一些严谨做法，比如测试、基准、迭代改进等等，这次引入Skills的创作流程。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 117
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "真的，牛逼太多了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 118
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "这绝对对于所有人来说，都是一个史诗级增强。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 119
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "你要知道，小龙虾为什么那么强，能做那么多的事，其实真不是因为他本身有多牛逼，纯粹是因为，它身上挂的SKills，太多了，那都是一个一个的技能包。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 120
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "可以说，Skills，就是整个Agent未来大繁荣生态的基石，而我自己，也一直极力的看好和强力推广各种各样的Skills。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 121
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "所以，我极度建议，大家把Skill-creator更新到最新版，然后把你自己所有的Skills，都进行优化和评估一遍。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 122
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "当然，你得先分清楚，你写的Skills是哪种。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 123
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "因为本质上，Skills其实分两种。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 124
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "第一种是能力提升型。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 125
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "就是教Claude做它本来不擅长的事。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 126
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "比如官方的前端设计skill、文档创建skill，里面写了大量技巧，是你光靠Prompt根本拿不到的效果。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 127
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "我们大多数人自己搓的skill，基本也都是这类。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 128
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "第二种官方叫编码偏好型。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 129
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "就是告诉Claude按你的规矩来。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 130
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "Claude本身每一步都能做，但你的skill把这些步骤按你团队的流程串起来了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 131
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "比如一个会议纪要整理skill，按你们公司固定的格式，自动把录音转成带行动项的文档。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 132
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "或者一个周报生成skill，从各个平台里拉数据，按你要的格式排好。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 133
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "你可以把这种，理解成一个Workflow，就是一个工作流。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 134
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "对这两种类型，评估的方向会稍微不太一样。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 135
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "对于能力提升型，测的是模型更新之后这个skill还有没有存在的必要。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 136
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "用A/B测试对比，有skill和没skill各跑一次。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 137
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "结果如果差不多，这个skill就可以退休了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 138
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "编码偏好型测的是另一件事，它有没有老老实实按你的流程走？",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 139
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "有没有漏步骤？有没有自作主张改了顺序？有没有忘了你特别说过的某个要求？",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 140
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "所以会稍稍有一些区别，这个大家在自己评估的时候，可以注意一下。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 141
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "回头想想，以前造完一个skill，其实也就是自我感觉良好。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 142
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "但说实话，全是黑盒，根本不知道该怎么评估。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 143
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "现在就舒服多了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 144
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "评估跑一遍，数据摆出来，好不好用，一眼就见真章。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 145
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "所有的Skills，真的都值得重新优化和评估一遍。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 146
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "Skills生态。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 147
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "感觉又要迎来一波大繁荣了。",
        "source": "/Users/cecilialiu/Documents/Codex/ai-content/viral_breakdowns/wx-vjMG8i7DwQ7R2B1C4AVQdA/download/article_body.txt",
        "line": 148
      },
      {
        "start": null,
        "end": null,
        "text": "以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。",
